arStrings.szText: Encroaching Shadows
Search for evidence of Lilith near Braestaig
Search for evidence of Lilith near Braestaig
Donan spoke of Lilith sightings near the home of Airidah, the elder druid. I should investigate the nearby town of Braestaig for clues.

I learned that fog and enraged spirits have descended on Braestaig from the northern hills. The druid watcher of the north, Airidah, has not been seen since the bedlam began. Yorin, Donan's son, says he can take me through the Weeping Cairns to reach the druid’s domain. Perhaps I can find more answers there?
